title: #140 - Ancient Ideas of Free Will
description: Once again, Connor and Dan are jumping in the way back machine. They're headed to Ancient Greece to see what those old fuddy duddys had to say about free will. Do the Gods decide our fate? Are we just cogs in a cause-and-effect machine? Or do we really have control over our actions? Who cares? Hopefully you! Also in this ep: Connor learns what a cutty bang is, Ewoks in metal bikinis, and a farewell to 2016. Enjoy!
